---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Mobula Music AS"
  description="Privacy policy for Mobula Music AS. Read how we process your personal data."
  lang="en"
  altLang="/personvern"
>
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6 text-cream/85 leading-relaxed">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-cream mt-8">Data controller</h2>
        <p>
          Mobula Music AS (org. no. 294554769) is the data controller for personal data collected via this website.
        </p>
        <p>
          Contact: <a href="mailto:post@mobulamusic.com" class="text-gold hover:underline">post@mobulamusic.com</a><br />
          Address: Fjellhammerveien 52, 1472 Fjellhamar, Norway
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-cream mt-8">What data do we collect?</h2>
        <p>
          When you fill in a contact form on our website, we collect your name, email address, phone number and message content. This information is used only to respond to your enquiry.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-cream mt-8">Purpose and legal basis</h2>
        <p>
          We process personal data to respond to enquiries and manage client relationships. The legal basis is consent (when submitting a form) and legitimate interest.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-cream mt-8">Storage and security</h2>
        <p>
          Personal data is stored for as long as necessary to fulfil the purpose of collection. We have implemented appropriate technical and organisational measures to secure the data.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-cream mt-8">Your rights</h2>
        <p>
          You have the right to access, correction, deletion and restriction of the processing of your personal data. Contact us at <a href="mailto:post@mobulamusic.com" class="text-gold hover:underline">post@mobulamusic.com</a> to exercise your rights.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-cream mt-8">Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          This website uses only necessary technical cookies. We do not use analytics or marketing cookies.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
